**When to use**: task specifies filling a range with computed values after analysis or counting

**Why it works**: Saving after writing persists the results and ensures the output artifact is delivered. Skipping this leaves the output empty even if calculations were performed correctly.

**Procedure**:
After writing any results to the sheet, explicitly save the output workbook to the required path.

